metadata.description:
The "Welcome to Nashville" anthem. Countrify ya life by adding this one to your Music NFT collection.

Produced by: Sam Martinez x Sammy Arriaga
Written by: Sammy Arriaga, Tim Riehm & Sam Martinez
Mix: Sam Martinez
Mastering: Nathan Dantzler (The Hitlab)

sammyarriaga.xyz

lyrics.text:
MUSIC CITY

INTRO HOOK
Take me down, down to Music City
Where the country girls
Looking so damn pretty,
And the bands are playing 
til the AM with me,
Hurry up and gas up the truck

V1
Man, **** work
Punched that clock so hard I done broke it
Got my check & I’m ready to blow it
I’m craving neon lights and a four-day holiday
(Yeah, yeah, yeah)

PRE1
Gettin’ the hell outta this two lane town
It ain’t my birthday but I like how that sounds
Call up the fellas cause we on our way out
Throw on an oldie, 
Light up a roadie and...

HOOK
Take me down, down to Music City
Where the country girls looking so damn pretty,
And the bands are playing til the AM with me,
Hurry up and gas up the truck
And take me down, down to Music City
Where the country girls ain’t afraid to get gritty,
And they drop a ben for some Tennessee Whiskey,
Hurry up and gas up the truck

V2:
Shit, I can’t wait
Bout to crash some bachelorettes
See how trashed we get
Promise we’ll forget everything
but I don’t care cause we doin it all again
Yeah yeah yeah...

PRE2
Don’t wanna go back to my two lane town
It ain’t my birthday but they buying me rounds
Even they momma gon’ be checkin’ me out
Whiskey & sodie, 
Play me an oldie and...

HOOK

CHANT
(No, No)
No I ain’t going back home (x4)

OUTRO HOOK:
Take me down to the Music City
Where the country girls looking so damn pretty,
And the bands are playing til the AM with me,
Hurry up and gas up the truck…
